entry.title: 2 Bedroom Maisonette, Hugon Road, SW6
entry.propertyDescription:
A spacious, two bedroom, furnished, split level flat in a terraced Victorian house. Large kitchen/breakfast room, living room, bathroom with power shower, separate WC and two double bedrooms with fitted wardrobes.

Nearest tube Fulham Broadway or Wandsworth Town British Rail. Buses 295,28 & C3.

Nearest train station Imperial Wharf or Wandsworth Town BR.
